---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Golf Cart Rentals - Masters Golf Cars" description="Reserve high-quality golf cart rentals for neighborhoods, events, and businesses across Central Florida.">
	<!-- Hero -->
	<section class="bg-white py-12">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
			<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-10">Golf Cart Rentals</h1>

			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-[1fr,0.9fr] gap-12 items-center">
				<div class="space-y-6">
					<h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Enjoy the Convenience of Golf Cart Rentals</h2>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
						Renting a golf cart from us is the perfect solution if you need reliable, affordable, and convenient transportation of a golf cart without the commitment of ownership. Whether you're planning for a quick getaway or a large event, we make it easier for you. Other customers come to us after facing issues with golf carts from other dealerships. While we repair their golf carts, they take advantage of our golf cart rental options, staying mobile without interruption. Renting a golf cart from us will give you peace of mind, whether for a short-term fix or a specific need.
					</p>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
						We have a minimum 3-day golf cart rental, with options for weekly or monthly rentals for individuals. We also offer golf cart rentals for businesses hosting events across Central Florida.
					</p>
					<ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
						<li>• Individual &amp; Event Rentals</li>
						<li>• Delivery &amp; Pick-Up Options</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl border border-gray-200 p-6">
					<img src="/images/golf-cart-rentals-page/golf-cart-rentals-in-the-villages_img_v69_250813_160043497.webp" alt="Golf cart rental" class="w-full h-auto rounded-2xl" loading="lazy" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Rental Options -->
	<section class="py-16 bg-white">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-10">Our Golf Rental Options</h2>
			<p class="text-center text-gray-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10">
				Choose from 2, 4, or 6 passenger golf carts along with utility models to fit your itinerary. Every cart is cleaned, inspected, and fully charged before it heads out the door.
			</p>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-6 md:gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
				<div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl shadow-md p-6">
					<img src="/images/golf-cart-rentals-page/2-seater-golf-cart_img_v63_250813_142814136.webp" alt="2-seater golf cart" class="mx-auto h-24 object-contain mb-4" loading="lazy" />
					<p class="font-semibold text-gray-800">2-Seater Cart</p>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl shadow-md p-6">
					<img src="/images/golf-cart-rentals-page/4-seater-golf-cart_img_v64_250813_142836603.webp" alt="4-seater golf cart" class="mx-auto h-24 object-contain mb-4" loading="lazy" />
					<p class="font-semibold text-gray-800">4-Seater Cart</p>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl shadow-md p-6">
					<img src="/images/golf-cart-rentals-page/6-seater-golf-cart_img_v65_250813_142855008.webp" alt="6-seater golf cart" class="mx-auto h-24 object-contain mb-4" loading="lazy" />
					<p class="font-semibold text-gray-800">6-Seater Cart</p>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl shadow-md p-6">
					<img src="/images/golf-cart-rentals-page/utility-cart_img_v66_250813_142912878.webp" alt="Utility golf cart" class="mx-auto h-24 object-contain mb-4" loading="lazy" />
					<p class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Utility Cart</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Models Banner -->
	<section class="py-12" style="background-color: #86CA26;">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
			<div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl px-8 py-10 flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-8">
				<div class="text-center lg:text-left">
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 uppercase tracking-wide">Golf Cart Models for Rent</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">Premium brands ready for neighborhoods, events, and commercial sites.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="flex items-center gap-8">
					<img src="/images/golf-cart-rentals-page/yamaha-logo-icon-0-0-250813163408273.webp" alt="Yamaha golf carts" class="h-16 object-contain" loading="lazy" />
					<img src="/images/golf-cart-rentals-page/club-car-logo-icon-0-1-250813163408445.webp" alt="Club Car golf carts" class="h-16 object-contain" loading="lazy" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- How Rentals Work -->
	<section class="py-16 bg-white">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
			<div class="grid lg:grid-cols-[1.15fr,0.85fr] gap-10 items-start">
				<div class="space-y-8">
					<img src="/images/golf-cart-rentals-page/yamaha-quietech-efi_img_v71_250813_161157847.webp" alt="Masters Golf Cars rental delivery" class="w-full max-w-3xl mx-auto h-auto rounded-[12px] shadow-md" loading="lazy" />
					<div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-[16px] shadow-md p-8 md:p-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
						<h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-5">How Our Golf Cart Rentals Work</h3>
						<ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-3 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
							<li>Complete the request form or call our rental specialists to get started.</li>
							<li>Select the cart that fits your needs — choose seat count, accessories, and roof styles.</li>
							<li>Reserve your rental with a minimal 3-day deposit (weekly &amp; monthly plans available).</li>
							<li>Secure your reservation with a credit card.</li>
							<li>We deliver to your location or you can pick up — and we’ll handle return details when you’re done.</li>
						</ol>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="flex justify-center">
					<img src="/images/golf-cart-rentals-page/rent-a-golf-cart_img_v72_250813_161858549.webp" alt="Rent a golf cart from Masters Golf Cars" class="w-full max-w-2xl h-auto rounded-[12px] shadow-md" loading="lazy" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Pricing & Terms -->
	<section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
			<div class="grid lg:grid-cols-[1.2fr,0.8fr] gap-10 items-center">
				<div class="bg-white rounded-[28px] shadow-lg border border-gray-200 p-8 md:p-10">
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Rental Pricing</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
						Our pricing structure is flexible for your schedule and budget. Submit the rental form or call our team for exact availability and a custom quote.
					</p>
					<h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Golf Cart Rental Terms &amp; Conditions</h4>
					<ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
						<li><span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Age Requirement:</span> Renters must be at least 21 years old.</li>
						<li><span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Agreement:</span> A valid rental contract is required to reserve your cart.</li>
						<li><span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Duration:</span> Minimum 3-day rentals; daily rentals available for certain events.</li>
						<li><span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Delivery &amp; Pick-Up:</span> Offered within 50 miles; extended service areas available by request.</li>
						<li><span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Service Area:</span> The Villages, Ocala, and surrounding Central Florida communities.</li>
					</ul>
					<div class="mt-8">
						<a href="/rentals" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 rounded-full bg-brand-green text-white font-bold uppercase tracking-wide hover:opacity-90 transition">Reserve Your Golf Cart Today</a>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="space-y-8">
					<img src="/images/golf-cart-rentals-page/club-car_img_v68_250813_154125925.webp" alt="Club Car golf cart rental" class="rounded-[32px] shadow-2xl w-full h-auto" loading="lazy" />
					<img src="/images/golf-cart-rentals-page/yamaha-quietech-efi_img_v71_250813_161157847.webp" alt="Yamaha golf cart rental" class="rounded-[32px] shadow-2xl w-full h-auto hidden lg:block" loading="lazy" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Why Rent -->
	<section class="py-16 bg-white">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
			<div class="grid lg:grid-cols-[0.85fr,1.15fr] gap-12 items-center">
				<div class="flex justify-center">
					<img src="/images/golf-cart-rentals-page/club-car_img_v68_250813_154125925.webp" alt="Premium golf cart rental" class="w-full max-w-xl h-auto rounded-[12px] shadow-md" loading="lazy" />
				</div>
				<div>
					<h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Why Rent A Golf Cart From Us?</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
						Masters Golf Cars delivers top-quality rentals from brands you know and trust. We maintain our fleet to dealership standards, so you get a clean, reliable ride every time — complete with accessories tailored to your plans.
					</p>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
						Our rental team handles everything from drop-off to pick-up, including charger setup, basic orientation, and on-call support during your rental window. We serve neighborhoods, resorts, weddings, festivals, corporate events, and commercial fleets across Central Florida.
					</p>
					<ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
						<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
							<span class="text-brand-green text-xl leading-none">•</span>
							<span>Flexible rental terms — daily, weekly, and monthly plans available.</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
							<span class="text-brand-green text-xl leading-none">•</span>
							<span>Fully serviced carts with options for windshields, enclosures, coolers, and lighting upgrades.</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
							<span class="text-brand-green text-xl leading-none">•</span>
							<span>Friendly customer support &amp; experienced delivery team.</span>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Reviews -->
	<section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
			<h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-12">Golf Cart Rental Reviews</h3>
			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
				<div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg p-8 border border-gray-100">
					<div class="mb-4 flex gap-1 text-brand-green">
						{Array.from({ length: 5 }).map((_star, index) => (
							<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
								<path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z" />
							</svg>
						))}
					</div>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
						“Fantastic people to work with. Delivered my rental cart on time as promised. Highly recommend!”
					</p>
					<p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Scott Lennox</p>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg p-8 border border-gray-100">
					<div class="mb-4 flex gap-1 text-brand-green">
						{Array.from({ length: 5 }).map((_star, index) => (
							<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
								<path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z" />
							</svg>
						))}
					</div>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
						“They were awesome to work with! They gave us an excellent deal on a rental while they fixed ours. The staff is extremely knowledgeable and professional.”
					</p>
					<p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Megan O’Brien</p>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg p-8 border border-gray-100">
					<div class="mb-4 flex gap-1 text-brand-green">
						{Array.from({ length: 5 }).map((_star, index) => (
							<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
								<path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z" />
							</svg>
						))}
					</div>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
						“The carts were delivered the day before, so we weren’t waiting on the day of. They performed the job and more. I would highly recommend renting carts from this great company with awesome staff.”
					</p>
					<p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Danielle Clark</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- FAQ -->
	<section class="py-16 bg-white">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
			<h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-10">Golf Cart Rentals FAQs</h3>
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-3">
				<details class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl px-5 py-4 shadow">
					<summary class="font-semibold text-gray-900 cursor-pointer">What is the minimum age to rent a golf cart?</summary>
					<p class="mt-3 text-gray-700">Renters must be at least 21 years old with a valid driver’s license and insurance.</p>
				</details>
				<details class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl px-5 py-4 shadow">
					<summary class="font-semibold text-gray-900 cursor-pointer">Can I rent a golf cart for an event?</summary>
					<p class="mt-3 text-gray-700">Absolutely. We support weddings, corporate gatherings, concerts, festivals, and multi-day sporting events with fleet rentals.</p>
				</details>
				<details class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl px-5 py-4 shadow">
					<summary class="font-semibold text-gray-900 cursor-pointer">Do I need to pay a deposit?</summary>
					<p class="mt-3 text-gray-700">Yes. A refundable deposit is required to secure your reservation and will be credited toward your rental balance.</p>
				</details>
				<details class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl px-5 py-4 shadow">
					<summary class="font-semibold text-gray-900 cursor-pointer">Can I extend my rental period?</summary>
					<p class="mt-3 text-gray-700">Most rentals can be extended with advance notice. Contact our team as soon as you know you’ll need additional time.</p>
				</details>
				<details class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl px-5 py-4 shadow">
					<summary class="font-semibold text-gray-900 cursor-pointer">Do you offer delivery for golf cart rentals?</summary>
					<p class="mt-3 text-gray-700">Yes, we deliver throughout Central Florida and offer convenient pickup options when you’re finished.</p>
				</details>
			</div>
			<div class="text-center mt-12">
				<a href="/rentals" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-10 py-4 rounded-full bg-brand-green text-white font-bold uppercase tracking-wide hover:opacity-90 transition">
					Rent Your Golf Cart Today
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

